## Not Found

```typescript
// apps/web/src/app/(dashboard)/users/[id]/not-found.tsx
export default function UserNotFound() {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 p-12">
      <p className="text-xl font-medium">User not found</p>
      <p className="text-gray-500">
        This user may have been deleted or you may not have access.
      </p>
      <a href="/users" className="btn btn-secondary">Back to Users</a>
    </div>
  );
}
```

---

## API Calls Made by This Page

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `GET /api/users/{id}` | GET | Load the entity |
| `GET /api/users/{id}/orders` | GET | Load related orders (first 5) |
| `DELETE /api/users/{id}` | DELETE | Triggered by DeleteDialog |
| `PATCH /api/users/{id}` | PATCH | Triggered by StatusToggle or InlineEditField |

