## Design Notes ({{ design_style }})

{% if design_style == "minimal-clean" %}
- Header: avatar placeholder (initials, gray circle), name in `text-2xl font-semibold`, email in `text-gray-500`
- Status badge: small pill, 2 colors only (green for active, gray for inactive)
- Details grid: two-column label/value layout, labels in `text-sm text-gray-500`, values in `text-sm font-medium`
- Danger zone: hidden behind a disclosure, red border section at the bottom
- No decorative elements - every visible element carries information
{% elif design_style == "corporate-professional" %}
- Header: professional avatar with colored border by role, name prominent, role/department visible
- Status badge: colored per status type (active/inactive/pending/suspended)
- Details grid: full-width card with section headers, alternating row backgrounds
- Action buttons: always visible, labeled (not icon-only)
- Danger zone: visible but with a warning icon and explanatory text
{% elif design_style == "playful-modern" %}
- Header: gradient avatar, name in bold with emoji status indicator
- Status badge: animated pulse dot + label, vibrant color per status
- Details grid: card per field group with hover effect and icons
- Action buttons: colored pill buttons with icons, hover animations
- Danger zone: accordion with a clear skull/warning icon, rounded-xl container
{% endif %}
